error.message: Class Drupal\memcache_storage\Tests\MemcacheStorageBackendUnitTest extends deprecated class Drupal\system\Tests\Cache\GenericCacheBackendUnitTestBase. Deprecated in drupal:8.2.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\KernelTests\Core\Cache\GenericCacheBackendUnitTestBase instead.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to memcache_storage.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
